        <p>T+S will not collect any personal information about you except when specifically and knowingly provided by
            you. Examples of such information are name, shipping and billing addresses, phone number, email address,
            credit card information and customer preferences data. Examples of ways in which we may collect such
            information from you include the following:
        <p>A.</p>
        <p>Registration and Ordering. Before using certain parts of this Site or ordering products, you must complete a
            registration form. When registering, you will be prompted to provide certain personal information, including
            but not limited to your name, shipping and billing addresses, phone number, email address, and credit card
