            processing your order, we will use the personal information to contact you.
        <p>B.
        <p>Email Addresses. Some areas of the Site allow you to enter your email address for purposes including, but not
            limited to opening a T+S account.
        <p>C.</p>
        <p>Cookies. Like most other websites,T+S uses cookie technology throughout this Site. A cookie is a small
